    <description>Get ready for a new and improved reference management experience.  
	- **Manage your references efficiently**: Your library now automatically syncs when you add references or make changes  
	- **Keep all your thoughts together** : Mendeley Notebook helps you collate all your highlights and notes from multiple PDFs  
	- **Cite seamlessly** : Also available: Mendeley Cite, the new citation add-in for Microsoft Word, takes the time out of referencing

**Please Note**: This is an automatically updated package. If you find it is out of date by more than a day or two, please contact the maintainer(s) and let them know the package is no longer updating correctly.</description>
    <summary>Considerable time and effort can be spent building and organizing your reference library, finding your references and notes when you need them and formatting citations correctly. The new Mendeley Reference Manager helps simplify these tasks, leaving you time to focus on achieving your goals.</summary>
    <releaseNotes>

## Mendeley Reference Manager v2.145.0

We have:

- added organisation and entitlement information display in the application
- improved keyboard navigation and screen reader support throughout the
      application


We have fixed:

- keyboard focus being lost after closing the Library Tag tree "More
      Actions" menu with the Escape key
- the Reading Assistant "Show More" citation buttons not conveying
      their purpose through their visible label
- the Right-Hand Panel tab list rendering above panel content
- light grey text in the Info Panel having insufficient colour contrast


## Support

- If you encounter any problems using Mendeley or have questions to ask
      please
      [contact our support team](https://www.mendeley.com/contact-support/ "Contact support").
- For news and updates about Mendeley see
      [our blog](http://blog.mendeley.com/).


Released: 20 May 2026




**Full changelog:** [https://www.mendeley.com/release-notes-reference-manager/v2.145.0](https://www.mendeley.com/release-notes-reference-manager/v2.145.0) </releaseNotes>
